title: SONGMICS Heavy-Duty Bin Bags, Drawstring Rubbish Bags for 13-Gallon (50L) Kitchen Bins, Pre-Separated, Liner Code 050A01, 3 Rolls, 120 Pieces, White KRB050A03
features: [Heavy-Duty] Made from 25 μm thick polyethylene, the body of each rubbish bag is strong enough to hold up to 25 kg. They are designed to resist tears, leaks, and punctures, so you won't have to worry about the bag falling apart on you

[Versatile] These heavy-duty bin bags excel in various roles, from packing belongings during a move to storing clothing during a big clean-up, or collecting leaves while pruning plants. They come in handy for a wide range of tasks
[Pre-Separated Bags] Easily take one bag at a time without tearing them apart as each bag is already separated in the pack, saving you the hassle of separating new bags from the roll!

[Convenient Drawstring Closure] Simply pull the drawstrings on both sides to tighten the trash bags and take out the rubbish. The drawstrings grip the bin rim without sliding down, and they also cinch up the bag nice and tight to trap icky smells
[Specs] These bin bags have a size of 59 x 74 cm and a volume of 50L. They come in 3 rolls of 40 pieces and are coded 050A01
